}  You can always manually stop recording events at any time by calling:  sdkbox::PluginGoogleAnalytics::stopSession();  However, in-order to record events again you must then manually call:  sdkbox::PluginGoogleAnalytics::startSession();  Logged data usually shows up within one day.

