#include  PluginTuneLuaHelper.h    Second, We need to register the plugin with Lua. This is done by making a call to  register_all_PluginTuneLua( lua_State* ); .   Note:  It is important to note that this call must be made after  lua_State *tolua_s = pStack- getLuaState();  and before  tolua_extensions_ccb_open(tolua_s); .  Here is an example of what this might look like for you:  #include  PluginTuneLua.hpp 
